INSERT INTO `%DB_PREFIX%msg_box` VALUES ('358','修改信息成功','【后台用户：admin】修改信息成功。','1','1415669215','2','2','UPDATE `tp_info` SET `pid`=29,`title`=\'金湧博发理财 值得打工族关注\',`img`=\'\',`imgs`=\'\',`url`=\'\',`tel`=\'\',`sort`=100,`click`=100,`time`=1415314330,`keyword`=\'\',`description`=\'\',`content`=\'<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :WordDocument><w :BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w :BrowserLevel><w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w :DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery><w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w :DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery><w :DocumentKind>DocumentNotSpecified</w :DocumentKind><w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8</w :DrawingGridVerticalSpacing><w :View>Normal</w :View><w :Compatibility><w :DontGrowAutofit/><w :BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/><w :DoNotExpandShiftReturn/><w :UseFELayout/></w :Compatibility><w :Zoom>0</w :Zoom></w :WordDocument></xml><![endif]--><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">打工族如何投资理财?相信很多投资者都有这样的想法。作为一名普通的上班族，我们经常会说花钱容易挣钱难。那么，如何才能使自己储蓄保值增值呢?唯有理财。通过对理财产品投资门槛、收益、风险、技术、灵活程度对比，不难发现</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">P2P</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">理财还是一个不错的投资方式。&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">　　</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">那么，打工族如何选择比较安全的P2P理财平台</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">呢?&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">　　</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">一、平台有无启用第三方资金托管。</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">该措施能有效防止平台资金池的形成，据说所有跑路的网贷没有一家是有第三方资金托管的。</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">金湧博发</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">与专业的第三方支付平台合作，保证客户的每一笔资金都安全，与实力雄厚的第三方担保公司合作，确保交易后资金的安全，并且可以实时查询到资金账户的详情</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">。</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">　　</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">二、可以从平台的技术和设计方面初步判断。</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">查看一下交易平台有无保障交易安全的加密技术。</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">金湧博发</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">拥有专业从事</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">金融</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">业软件开发和系统集成的IT技术团队</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">，</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">为网站平台提供先进、科学、严谨的应用软件以及整体解决方案。我们运用专业的防</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">DDoS</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">设备来抵御攻击，同时还启用侵扰监测系统来监测那些内部和外部易受侵扰的路径，双机热备份模式保证实时数据备份和主机内容安全，并运用云安全技术和其他一些人工措施来加强保护数据安全。&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">　　</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">三、</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">风控系统要安全。</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">从平台借款人信息公开情况以及逾期率控制情况，了解平台风控团队是否具有金融背景，是否有良好的风险控制能力，目前口碑比较好的是</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">金湧博发</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">理财，据说他们平台的坏账率是全行业最低的，每月的还款率达85%，整整高于同行业15个百分点。&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">　　</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">四、查看平台风险保障制度(有无本金或本息的保障协议)从中了解平台对于逾期借款的垫付能力。</span><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"./\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">金湧博发</span></a><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">完善的风险代偿金制度为您提供本金保障，为您的资金安全保驾护航。</span><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">如果第三方坏账，金湧博发将无条件偿还投资者本息。这样可以让投资者享受安全投资，保障收益。</span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br/></span></p><p class=\\\"p0\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:&#39;yes&#39;;font-weight:normal;font-size:14.0000pt;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;\\\">打工族们不要再把时间浪费在到哪里去投资上，P2P理财才是最适合打工一族的理财方式。投资理财那加强，中国东北找金湧！</span></p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><w :LatentStyles deflockedstate=\\\"false\\\" defunhidewhenused=\\\"true\\\" defsemihidden=\\\"true\\\" defqformat=\\\"false\\\" defpriority=\\\"99\\\" latentstylecount=\\\"260\\\"><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"Normal\\\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"heading 1\\\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"heading 2\\\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"heading 3\\\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"heading 4\\\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"heading 5\\\"></w :LsdException><w :LsdException locked=\\\"false\\\" priority=\\\"99\\\" semihidden=\